ChangeLog: Fix ChangeLog entry.

	* gcc/ChangeLog: Fix ChangeLog entry.
	* gcc/c/ChangeLog: Ditto.
	* gcc/c-family/ChangeLog: Ditto.
	* gcc/cp/ChangeLog: Ditto.

-	warn_for_restrict.
-cp/
